  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Hex</em></p>\n<p>You manifest a mantle of malevolent dark side energy for the duration.</p>\n<p>Until the power ends, any attack you make deals an extra [[/r 1d8]] necrotic damage when you hit a creature within 10 feet of you. Any creature that takes this damage can't regain hit points until the start of your next turn.</p>\n<p>Additionally, any creature of your choice that you can see that starts its turn within 10 feet of you gains 1 slowed level until the start of your next turn.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Force Potency.</em></strong> When you cast this power using a force slot of 5th level or higher, the extra damage increases by [[/r 1d8]] for for every two slot levels above 3rd.</p>",
